<img alt="Warning" src="/style/images/warning.png" /></div><div style="display:table-cell">
<p>To select Unit of Assessment Champions a user must first be assigned the <strong>ref/select_champions</strong> role.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div>

<h3>REF1 Profile Information</h3>
<p>Staff identified as taking part in your REF submission will have an enhanced profile, where REF1 data can be provided. This information will be used to generate the REF1 report.</p>

<p>Staff may be allocated to one Unit of Assessment, enabling them to make submissions to that panel specifically.</p>

<p>To edit a user's REF1 Profile Information, go to their user profile and click "<epc:phrase ref="Plugin/Screen/REF_Support/User/Edit:title"/>"</p>

<h3>Identify REF2 Outputs</h3>
<p>Staff identified as taking part in your REF submission will be able to select their research outputs to be submitted to their assigned assessment panel. Additional REF2 data can be provided against each selection, including a self-rating and additional information for the panel to consider.</p>

<div class="ep_msg_other"><div class="ep_msg_other_content"><div style="border-spacing:5px; display:table"><div style="display:table-row"><div style="display:table-cell; vertical-align:middle;">
<img alt="Warning" src="/style/images/warning.png" /></div><div style="display:table-cell">
<p>In order to make a selection, a user must first be assigned the <strong>ref/select</strong> role.</p>
